WhereKept helps you remember where important household items are stored in your home and works as a simple item locator for daily use.

Save item details such as item name, room, drawer, storage place, and notes so you can quickly find stored items whenever needed.

The app works fully offline and stores data locally on your device, making it a practical offline storage app for privacy and convenience.

You can use WhereKept as a home organizer and household tracker to manage documents, chargers, keys, warranty papers, passports, household tools, and other personal belongings in one searchable list.

Features:
• Add and save household items
• Search items instantly
• Organize by room and storage location
• Offline local storage
• Simple and lightweight interface

WhereKept also helps as a home inventory tool by making everyday household item management simple, fast, and easy.
